From: Ian Rogers <irogers@google.com>
Date: Thu, 2 Oct 2025 15:07:26 -0700
Subject: perf stat: Move create_perf_stat_counter() to builtin-stat.c
Git-commit: 6026ab657a0e9e8b05f8d9fbf99a65151ce7a40b
Patch-mainline: v6.18-rc1
References: perf-sle16.1-v6.19-userspace-update

The function create_perf_stat_counter is only used in builtin-stat.c
and contains logic about retrying events specific to
builtin-stat.c.

Move the code to builtin-stat.c to tidy this up.

